Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyun Jun and Sa Woo are in the Special Forces,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and they are as close as blood brothers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyun Jun, on orders from his superiors,\Nattends graduate school where he meets Seung Hee.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He falls for her at first sight,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but suddenly, Seung Hee disappears without\Na word, which sends him into depression.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hometown friend introduces Seung Hee to\NSa Woo, and he, as well, falls for her at first sight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then one day, Hyun Jun and Sa Woo,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are taken by strange men to a place,\Nwhere they are put through harsh tests.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After finishing an intensive training,\Nthey become a part of the NSS.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On their first day of reporting,\Nthey see Seung Hee again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fact that she intentionally\Nfooled them makes them angry,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but they can't shake off their feelings for her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seung Hee coldly draws the line in their relationship,\Nbut Hyun Jun forcefully kisses her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The two of them become close quickly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The first assignment Hyun Jun and Sa Woo received,\Nis to follow  a terrorist named Dackasi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}During the course of their assignment,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:01:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they end up saving the life of the front\Nrunning presidential candidate, Jo Myung Ho.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop playing around and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for him to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The President is on his way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The President is on his way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Hyun Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to be when you grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who protects the world, Superman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are both nuclear scientists from MIT{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with complete knowledge of nuclear fusion.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They need to die.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think my friend is a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Jin Sa Woo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kim Hyun Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the two of you,\NI can stand here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We only did our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you're not of the Secret Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then are you a part of the National Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... we're actually part of the NSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,NSS?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:04:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will explain to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pigeon heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting the president had you that nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But, hey... it seemed like the President\Ndidn't know about the NSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first I'm hearing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just recently learned of the NSS myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,NSS was first established in 1976.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, the central intelligence\Nwas in charge of all the top secret affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But there were double agents working with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,both our intelligence and the American CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They wired the Blue House for monitoring
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and had it under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You are aware that the former President,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Park Chung Hee was developing nuclear arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the country needed an agency to operate
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,away from the prying eyes of the US government.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That is how the NSS came to be established.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The development of nuclear arms was under NSS operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after the change in administration,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,not only did they protect the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but protected the safety of the nation's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1996, it was the NSS that killed Choi Gwon Shik's assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1997, it was the NSS that tracked down the murderer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.18,0:05:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,from North Korea, Lee Young Ahn,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,followed him to Dandong, China and killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.09,0:05:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a Congressman who worked with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the National Intelligence for 12 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So for someone like me to have never heard of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,such an organization, can that make any sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The NSS is a secret organization even from domestic intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside of it, there aren't many people\Nthat are privy to its operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They are even utilizing the Russian\Nsatellites for intelligence gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, it goes without saying that neither
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the US nor Japan knows about its existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it is an operation that needs to continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It will prove itself to be very beneficial to you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,during your administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, does he want it dismantled?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:07:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A person like him will need more time to make his decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Should he ask you about it, tell him\Nyou see the need for the NSS to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My thoughts on that are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no need for your thoughts right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahjumma, one more bottle here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.79,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How was the visit to the Blue House?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... it was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo is going around saying you were
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,so nervous that you couldn't even talk straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you really like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, even Kim Hyun Jun freezes in front of the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not doing anything,\Ngo with me somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to get some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You grew up in a cathedral?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There, that orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were doing the background check on me and Sa Woo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that information would have been in the files.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Your background file only included information
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,from after you enlisted in the Special Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked for information previous to that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but the higher office said I didn't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I did think it a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here when I was 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed here until Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,During High School and College,\NI rented a room near the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What about before then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I have no memory of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's actually what I came here today to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Michael!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard anything from you\Nso I thought you wrote me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After being discharged from the army,\Nthen I got a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have the chance to come visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this here is a friend of mine from my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Choi Seung Hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to marry her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but our relationship hasn't reached that point yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you like the company you work for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here today because there's\Nsomething I would like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I end up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And what were my parents like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know anything then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never once asked this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you curious about it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious myself as to why\NI never once thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I tried to bury everything in my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that happened to me before I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was even one memory,\NI may not be so curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's like I have amnesia,\NI don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I find it strange that\Nthe whole time I was growing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,these thoughts never entered my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think it's like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are my parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The person that brought you here was a city worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no information about you or your background.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as if you were traumatized by something,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't speak a single word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... it was about a year that passed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,before you began to adjust to the life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He said there was no information or records.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The NSS doesn't have any information on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and if there is nothing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then maybe you just fell from the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy Mother, is it okay for me to love someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,who is full of secrets like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She said what difference does the past make?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyun Jun was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He was curious about his parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and how he ended up coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't seem like he knew anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you receive the word?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Blue House is asking to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been with the NSS since its inception?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In all honesty, I have my doubts on whether\Nwe still need an operation like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we still need it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe that's a judgment I can make.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We only carry out the orders of the President,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,even if we have to put our lives on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We do not make any decisions on political issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you one final question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that during Park Chung Hee's administration,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,nuclear weapons were being developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How far did we get with the technology?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I know, nuclear weapons\Nwere developed to completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When the new administration came into office,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,they wanted to win the favor of the US Government,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so they voluntarily gave up the development of nuclear weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The information to build nuclear arms to completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The program to develop them\Nmay have been abandoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but the knowledge couldn't have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That was not my area of responsibility,\Nso I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it some...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunbae-nim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Section Chief is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure but you should hurry over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ask to see us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, they told me to give you guys a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't do anything so I don't know\Nwhy they think you deserve a vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We saved the President's life.\NHow is that nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just pure luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm embarrassed to tell anyone about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know luck is also skill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo.  Don't you think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to look at you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?  I don't know yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Seung Hee?\NYou have plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we won't have a chance like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish the three of us could go on a trip somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, Mother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Trip to Japan, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've confirmed it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll begin immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust us and just try to relax a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.77,0:18:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kim Il Joong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They've found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They've found out where I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shao Wang, answer me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the car ready to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The front's blocked.\NWe'll have to go through the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it'll be difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll need to put our hopes on Hong Seung Ryong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have guards on me around the clock,\NI can't contact the South...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the IRIS list you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there's only Hong Seung Ryong left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, it's your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hong Seung Ryong,\Na member of the 131 Labor Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As you well know, the nuclear weapons program is,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,under the jurisdiction of the 131 Labor Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hong Seung Ryong is a key person\Nin the party for the nuclear program.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean key person?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please explain in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the head nuclear scientist\Nin the weapons development.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For what reason is he seeking political asylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This all came about so suddenly that\Nwe haven't had the chance to assess that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.13,0:22:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the route for the defection and the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He is currently in Ukraine,\Nbut I believe he will soon enter Hungary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hungary?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.11,0:22:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it so hard today?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.99,0:22:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hwang Tae Sung!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.23,0:22:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.55,0:22:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Call back the agents from vacation immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.28,0:22:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.69,0:22:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on Orange Alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and bring them in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.88,0:22:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Orange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.26,0:23:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.71,0:23:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.  It's really beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyun Jun, come and look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.38,0:23:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see the entire lake. Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.23,0:23:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyun Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:23:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:24:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.31,0:24:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's wash up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.91,0:24:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.00,0:24:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so dirty minded...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.42,0:24:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}Although you flow from my own two eyes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.08,0:24:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}you cannot see me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.17,0:24:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}Although my lips call you calmly,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.13,0:24:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.24,0:24:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard there was a famous hot spring around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.57,0:24:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us how to get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.41,0:24:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}you cannot hear me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.53,0:24:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}If we had met and loved{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.98,0:24:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get to the village over there,\Nit's the house at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.25,0:24:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.57,0:25:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}during different times, a different place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.25,0:25:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}would we be happy right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.52,0:25:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}For the rest of my life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.82,0:25:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}it should have been you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.74,0:25:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.23,0:25:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}but now it will only be{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.52,0:25:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.72,0:25:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}my staggering figure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.43,0:25:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}Since I can't hate you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.82,0:25:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}or forget you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.32,0:25:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}I guess there's nothing left{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.60,0:25:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.66,0:25:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly as I'd imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.10,0:25:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}for me to do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.15,0:25:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.86,0:25:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted and I'm just going to\Nsit and soak to my heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.73,0:25:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}other than to love you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.91,0:25:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.86,0:25:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.15,0:26:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.02,0:26:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to leave for Hungary immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.89,0:26:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,By myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.12,0:26:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyun Jun and Seung Hee should go with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.90,0:26:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can't get in touch with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.69,0:26:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.76,0:26:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as we get a hold of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.84,0:26:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll send them right behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.05,0:26:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You go ahead and leave right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.33,0:26:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You will receive your assignment once you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.74,0:26:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's meet right there when we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.34,0:26:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See you in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.19,0:26:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.15,0:26:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.04,0:26:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.46,0:27:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I went out the correct door.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.44,0:27:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.28,0:27:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you were mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.76,0:27:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this door is the right exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.87,0:28:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.71,0:28:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.72,0:28:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.02,0:28:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said you were going\Nto soak to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.90,0:28:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.21,0:28:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.80,0:28:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of soaking the body,\Nsoaking the feet is much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.95,0:28:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh brother... how can a man be that shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.94,0:28:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What, me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.88,0:28:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.38,0:28:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?  It's that school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.88,0:28:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.11,0:28:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.61,0:28:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.82,0:28:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.78,0:28:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.30,0:29:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.72,0:29:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.00,0:29:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.04,0:29:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hwang Tae Sung!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.58,0:29:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened with Kim Hyun Jun and Choi Seung Hee?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.85,0:29:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still trying to get in contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.01,0:29:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer will you just call?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.92,0:29:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Send someone and bring them in right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.53,0:29:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.97,0:29:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is truly Snowland.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.84,0:29:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we're in one of Kawabata Yasunari's novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.64,0:30:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I see snow,\Nit makes me grit my teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.15,0:30:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think of the times,\Nwe had to walk on snowy roads
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.51,0:30:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,during training in the Special Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.05,0:30:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.53,0:30:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure know how to break the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.27,0:30:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.38,0:30:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'm curious about.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.76,0:30:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.73,0:30:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you kiss me so suddenly that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.07,0:30:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it a challenge or was it love?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.01,0:31:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... it wasn't just a kiss,\Nbut it was because,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.82,0:31:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,from those beautiful lips of yours,\Ncrude words were pouring out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.97,0:31:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to shut it for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.65,0:31:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... I will have to say\Nlots of crude things from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.40,0:31:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.03,0:32:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jin Sa Woo from South Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.36,0:32:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.33,0:34:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.42,0:35:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, there was something I needed to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.01,0:35:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here for just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.12,0:35:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyun Jun and Seung Hee,\Nto remember just us two on a trip.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.50,0:35:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.33,0:35:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like childish things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.01,0:36:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.62,0:36:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.09,0:36:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.11,0:36:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop beating around the bush\Nand just give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.84,0:36:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you buy that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.94,0:36:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.40,0:36:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's there to be so shy about between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.09,0:36:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't bring any underclothes either?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.29,0:36:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,These are men's,\Nwill they be okay for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.67,0:36:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to wear them, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.48,0:37:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you by any chance....\Nexpect candy for White Day?*
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.48,0:37:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\a6}(*Korean Valentine's Day){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.68,0:37:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god, you're driving me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.60,0:37:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this funny to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.02,0:37:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so childish, like a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.46,0:37:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I or did I not say\NI like childish things?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.02,0:37:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.15,0:37:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you playing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.52,0:38:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're empty handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.72,0:39:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, are you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.74,0:40:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sleep on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.55,0:40:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's uncomfortable over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.76,0:40:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you give me my pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.05,0:40:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.94,0:40:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.64,0:40:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift your head for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.67,0:41:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.83,0:41:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.27,0:41:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.33,0:41:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because I miss your laughter that I hear whenever{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.28,0:41:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the cold wind brushes the tips of my fingers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.00,0:41:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your two eyes that reflected my face,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.43,0:41:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because I'm lonely, I cry and cry again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.51,0:41:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The words I couldn't say,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.73,0:41:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as my lips were frozen{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.94,0:42:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.29,0:42:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was famished.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.89,0:42:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.75,0:42:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You do things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.20,0:42:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really thoughtful like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.59,0:43:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.67,0:43:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.88,0:43:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the first time\Nyou've seen a pretty girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.51,0:43:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just eat your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.29,0:43:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time\NI've seen your face turn red.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.79,0:43:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although you flow from my own two eyes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.51,0:43:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you cannot see me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.67,0:43:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although my lips call you calmly,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.88,0:44:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you cannot hear me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.07,0:44:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we had met and loved during{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.07,0:44:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}different times, a different place,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.82,0:44:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}would we be happy right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.01,0:44:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the rest of my life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.51,0:44:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it should have been you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.72,0:44:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.41,0:44:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it will only be my staggering figure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.15,0:44:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since I can't hate you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.37,0:44:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or forget you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.87,0:44:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess there's nothing left for me to do,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.20,0:44:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}other than to love you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.28,0:45:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Team Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.62,0:45:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry in to the conference room.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.74,0:45:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.12,0:45:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They've just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.26,0:45:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.  I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.04,0:45:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.20,0:45:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're on vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.66,0:46:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it basic procedure\Nto leave the emergency line open?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.25,0:46:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.03,0:46:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How much have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.31,0:46:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.96,0:46:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These are tickets to Hungary.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.07,0:46:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.99,0:46:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hong Seung Ryong.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.93,0:46:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He heads the nuclear research in North Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.68,0:46:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He is requesting political asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.19,0:46:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.37,0:46:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in Hungary,\Nunder protection of one of our agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.34,0:46:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone like that to suddenly seek political asylum,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.26,0:46:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't we be suspicious of his true intent?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.95,0:46:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Additionally, granting the asylum is a very\Ntouchy issue during these sensitive times.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.20,0:46:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to be especially careful, so that it'll not cause\Nmisunderstanding with the North or worse, war.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.43,0:46:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to hear your opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.04,0:47:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We've put agents to try and find out his true intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.49,0:47:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you should wait to hear the results\Nbefore you make your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.26,0:47:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer honestly to the questions I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.33,0:47:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.01,0:47:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go for vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.27,0:47:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan. Akita.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.83,0:47:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there someone who went with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.09,0:47:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.67,0:48:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Seung Hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.45,0:48:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.57,0:48:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.17,0:48:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.93,0:48:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's already someone that you've\Navowed your love for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.96,0:48:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you met in graduate school a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.08,0:48:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Seung Hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.54,0:48:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first person I told about this,\Nso you have to keep the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.31,0:48:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep my mouth shut,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.97,0:48:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but do you think a relationship\Nwith your superior will be easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.50,0:48:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.12,0:48:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When this assignment is over,\NI want to have her stop working.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.75,0:48:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.37,0:48:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sa Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.81,0:49:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the two of us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.34,0:49:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made a difficult decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.43,0:49:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'll need to assess your true intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.16,0:49:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for requesting political asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.15,0:49:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I ask questions that you find difficult,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.31,0:49:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.67,0:49:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You attended the nation's top\Njunior and high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.08,0:49:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you graduated from Kim Il Sung University,\Nhaving majored in Physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.49,0:50:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And you received your Doctorate from Germany's LMU.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.30,0:50:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You were academically quite elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.56,0:50:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The watch you're wearing,\Nis it about 20 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.11,0:50:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't welcome change\Nand faithfully resist external influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.75,0:50:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the type to stay true to your organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.81,0:50:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure your belief and trust\Nin your party must have been great.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.06,0:50:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,As great as your involvement in the 131 Labor Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.92,0:51:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you've been waiting a long time for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.50,0:51:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,so she's that much more precious to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.64,0:51:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know well\Nwhat will happen to the two of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.96,0:51:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because of your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.62,0:51:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.82,0:51:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.52,0:51:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The assessment results are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.54,0:51:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It must not be an easy decision for them to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.15,0:51:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, the political impact will be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.14,0:52:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.08,0:52:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I will be able to go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.18,0:52:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.02,0:52:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not something we can decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.63,0:52:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way do you think he will go?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.56,0:52:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think he will reject the request?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.23,0:52:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Political issues are never that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.31,0:52:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.95,0:52:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The President is asking to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.52,0:52:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to permit the asylum
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.27,0:53:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The political fallout might be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.48,0:53:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.84,0:53:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to meet Hong Seung Ryong.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.24,0:53:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a great interest in nuclear arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.16,0:53:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And if at all possible,\NI would like to retrieve,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.63,0:53:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the previous nuclear research knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.27,0:53:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No word yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.21,0:53:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.32,0:53:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's so awkward in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.34,0:53:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why haven't they given us any word yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.76,0:53:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you went to Japan for vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.96,0:53:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyun Jun told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.92,0:53:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.88,0:54:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How can an agent talk so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.71,0:54:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyun Jun says he wants to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.19,0:54:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we get married right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.86,0:54:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That Kim Hyun Jun's overreacting is really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.76,0:54:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So... if not now, then at some point,\Ndo you want to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.81,0:54:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing the work we do,\Nit's hard to make plans for the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.41,0:54:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but when the time's right, I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.72,0:55:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Hyun Jun from the top of his head to the tips of his toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.97,0:55:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy is full of flaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.61,0:55:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Think carefully before you decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.56,0:55:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.41,0:55:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I'm an expert\Nwhen it comes to flaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.04,0:55:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a religion?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.24,0:55:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.97,0:55:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.75,0:55:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.46,0:55:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed in my God when I left the North,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.18,0:55:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but the agent from the South does not,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.14,0:55:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,what an irony that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.19,0:55:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.19,0:55:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Live as if there is a God.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.72,0:56:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a God,\Nthen you will gain eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.31,0:56:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is no God,\Nthen you will lose nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.62,0:56:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.37,0:56:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.65,0:56:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They've made their decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.40,0:56:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We will escort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.40,0:57:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.68,0:58:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why here of all places?\NIt's so in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.44,0:58:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hungary is Europe's belly button.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.22,0:58:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fly out of this belly button,\Nyou can go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.87,0:58:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Switzerland, Paris, Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.52,0:58:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.46,0:59:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful on your journey.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.26,1:00:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... who are you?
